  abilityName: Shattering Charge
  description: "Once per day, make a solo mounted charging\nAttack with a lance.\nThe
    Attack gains +d12, Blast , and Gambits\ncaused by the Attack count as strong.\nThe
    lance is shattered.\nPASSION - Adventure\nRestore SPI when you enter a Myth Hex.\nSteed
    agasp, spear agroan, strike agore\nSharp afrail, sight ablind, then no more\nLance
    Knight\nMYSTIC SIGHT\nWhat can you see? But you cannot see\n1 Fears Colour\n2
    Desires Writing\n3 Hidden things Birds\n4 Regrets Water\n5 Loyalties Stars and
    sun\n6 Injuries and disease Silver and gold\nKNIGHTED BY...\nThe Shackled Seer\nVIG
    10, CLA 16, SPI 13, 3 GD\n\u2022 Has a strange number of limbs (d12),\nseemingly
    changing with each glimpse,\nall shackled to the wall.\n\u2022 Has especially
    clear visions of things that\nwish to be elsewhere.\n\u2022 Pleads for freedom,
    but just wants to be\nshackled somewhere new.\nPerson: Puny guard ~ Name: Howell
    ~ Characteristic: Sulky and unwashed\nObject: Plague scabbard ~ Beast: Clawed
    bees ~ State: Awestruck ~ Theme: Touch\n3\n9\nThe"
